com.hazelcast.internal.memory

Interface ByteAccessStrategy<R>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - - type of external resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConcurrentHeapMemoryAccessor, GlobalMemoryAccessor, HeapMemoryAccessor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlignmentAwareMemoryAccessor, ByteArrayAccessStrategy, CustomByteAccessStrategy, StandardMemoryAccessor

    public interface ByteAccessStrategy<R>
    Access strategy for single memory bytes. Specifies the minimum contract for endianness-aware operations.
